title: Philippines CPI Housing & Utilities
description: CPI Housing Utilities in Philippines increased to 115.10 points in October from 114.60 points in September of 2022. CPI Housing Utilities in Philippines averaged 106.81 points from 2012 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 115.10 points in October of 2022 and a record low of 97.90 points in January of 2012. This page provides - Philippines  Cpi Housing & Utilities- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Philippine Statistics Authority
